{"tid":2133840,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"認住佢地 - 左丁山","createTime":"2020-07-31T10:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T10:39:16.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e4ff980a173b2202eed852872405435964e065d7","tid":2133840,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:26:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200717/NXH4OSBZ2NE5XKP55QED6M6SEE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200717%2FNXH4OSBZ2NE5XKP55QED6M6SEE%2F&d=LJfbHi1nzQR09hbgKwAG1%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=75ac38da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200717%2FNXH4OSBZ2NE5XKP55QED6M6SEE%2F&h=2ff2d6f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200717/NXH4OSBZ2NE5XKP55QED6M6SEE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n認住佢地 - 左丁山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8JPMh79j7AZQtf8EZ0VfCOFOkS0=/5030x3353/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TGWMCKFY2JBXBIVRF6EF4GB6MU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8JPMh79j7AZQtf8EZ0VfCOFOkS0%3D%2F5030x3353%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTGWMCKFY2JBXBIVRF6EF4GB6MU.jpg&h=e5cb3f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前左丁山寫過建制派未選先怯，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n選舉主任咁快開槍，。。。。。。。。。。選舉主任有五位最快有行動：<br />\n<br />\n（一）新界東地方選區選舉主任楊蕙心<br />\n<br />\n（二）新界西地方選區選舉主任黃展翹<br />\n<br />\n（三）九龍西地方選區選舉主任梁子琪<br />\n<br />\n（四）香港島地方選區選舉主任黃智華<br />\n<br />\n（五）法律界功能組別選舉主任莫君虞<br />\n<br />\n呢五位勤力用功嘅選舉主任在7月25日星期六。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。正如一啲中環deal maker諗到一條妙計玩財技，但公司律師話法律上未必許可，老闆就會講：「咁高薪請你做乜，同我死掂佢！」（按：左丁山曾親耳聽過呢類說話。）曾鈺成係政治師爺款，話唔定西環會受落，下令相關人等：「延期就延期，你地死掂佢！」老實講，如果諗住實贏，講咁多嘢做乜噃，仲要元老級人馬譚耀宗、曾鈺成厚住面皮嚟講，加埋選舉主任閃電出擊㖭。哈，居然有人死掂佢，話將延期選舉之事交畀人大常委決定喎，識自閹而自肥，可以考試第一。"},{"pid":"1cf02e5c1e289fcd0474456655b0c712468c404b","tid":2133840,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:35:58.000Z","msg":"仲有DQ岑敖暉呢個呀唔好漏咗佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05WZXjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05WZXjG.jpg&h=761a9e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PEBrCjG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPEBrCjG.jpg&h=3799e3cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7zbK8rk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7zbK8rk.jpg&h=02feb940&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c80921b62a611dc32fef8b8bb4a7d25e7c752ea6","tid":2133840,"uid":123905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T10:39:16.000Z","msg":"左丁山唔係藍屍咩？"}]}